comments: Ariza (MIA) makes marginal contact with White (CHI) as he has a resting hand on his back while contesting the driving shot attempt.
Dragic (MIA) places a forearm against Theis' (CHI) back and marginal contact occurs that does not affect Theis' ability to finish the play at the rim.
Theis (CHI) makes contact with the ball and delays the Heat from inbounding the ball after the made basket.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of White (CHI) firms up  and absorbs the contact.
Vincent (MIA) avoids making contact to the arm of Vucevic (CHI) and cleanly dislodges the ball from him during the drive.
Vucevic (CHI) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Dragic (MIA) that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) places a hand on Temple's (CHI) hip and marginal contact occurs as Temple loses control of the ball.
White (CHI) avoids making contact to Butler's (CHI) body during his driving shot attempt in transition.
Vincent (MIA) commits a take foul on White (CHI).
Ariza (MIA) grabs the arm of White (CHI) at the start of his drive on the perimeter.
Strus (MIA) makes contact to the arm of Williams (CHI) after he has secured the rebound.
Dragic (MIA) commits a take foul on White (CHI).
